{"tid":1124773,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【復仇者聯盟4】內地網友睇完即送院急救　網友：入戲太深！","createTime":"2019-04-25T08:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T10:44:07.000Z","uid":122110,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"59e63ca7d8b30e6827bf241e9d226c3c7c0a230f","tid":1124773,"uid":122110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:39:03.000Z","msg":"Source： <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/321924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F321924&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5ScRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=990009d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/321924</a><br />\n<br />\n據內地媒體《新京報》報道，在24日凌晨，有一位來自浙江寧波的21歲女生，在看完《復仇者4》後突發胸悶氣促、手指抽筋，甚至出現痙攣現象，五隻手指完全打不開，似雞爪一般，因而被送往醫院急救。經醫生診斷，這位觀眾因為觀影時哭得太傷心，一直大口喘氣，造成換氣過度。醫生表示，通過安撫患者情緒放鬆，吸氧或者戴口罩，減少換氣頻率，即可緩解症狀。<br />\n<br />\n有網友表示：「看個電影至於嗎？」、「姊妹入戲太深」、「看一下心理醫生吧」，不過也有網友認為每個人情緒不同，情有可原：「人與人本來就不一樣，你能承受不一定別人能承受，發言前先學習尊重」、「可能是真粉吧」、「看到能觸動自己的點就能哭啊」等等。<br />\n<br />\n以前笑dc so dark，而家睇mcu都要心理輔導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b2702712f37cfe282b7d8c2ba201f0b9e03753","tid":1124773,"uid":122110,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:41:28.000Z","msg":"睇完真係好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a125dd554ad59204a084be09aba60e14e9ae02","tid":1124773,"uid":122110,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:54:25.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇完都好空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47074cb55ee4a8dbfd9e79051744bf1a3fb38d1","tid":1124773,"uid":25345,"like":7,"dislike":13,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:38:16.000Z","msg":"鄧佢老母難過 生個智障女 睇個公仔片攪到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h